{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-excerpt-js","path":"/excerpts/nature_winter_solstice/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>It's clear that the darkness has won,<br>\nIt's dark from evening till mid morn,<br>\nThe sun just clips the horizon,<br>\nOne fears there'll never be a dawn,<br>\nIn time the sun's to be more strong,<br>\nA rebalancing will begin,<br>\nAn end to a pendulum swing,<br>\nThe darkness will stop devouring,<br>\nFrom the sun we have turned away,<br>\nWe now see the error of our ways,<br>\nA grave imbalance has been made,<br>\nDusk is early and dawn is late,<br>\nWe've a season till real change,<br>\nIt's bleak and tomorrow's the same,<br>\nWe scarcely see the light of day,<br>\nThis darkness takes an age to fade.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 17, 2020","title":"Winter Solstice","audio":{"publicURL":"/static/f107b7635c4be49b5775d027b595a7e6/Christian Lacdael - Nature - 17 Winter Solstice.mp3"},"icon":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/c8c2dc81835d0de4a3cb25a5c5eacd78/3c17d/winter_solstice.png","srcSet":"/static/c8c2dc81835d0de4a3cb25a5c5eacd78/69585/winter_solstice.png 200w,\n/static/c8c2dc81835d0de4a3cb25a5c5eacd78/497c6/winter_solstice.png 400w,\n/static/c8c2dc81835d0de4a3cb25a5c5eacd78/3c17d/winter_solstice.png 720w","sizes":"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/excerpts/nature_winter_solstice/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}